<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{#if lang}}{{lang}}{{else}}fr{{/if}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>{{#eq lang "en"}}FASO ADMIN — Session revoked{{else}}FASO ADMIN — Session révoquée{{/eq}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f6f4;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f6f4;padding:32px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;padding:28px 32px;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;">FASO ADMIN</h1>
            <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#FFD700;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Active session revoked{{else}}Session active révoquée{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px;color:#222;">
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}One of your active sessions has just been revoked.{{else}}L'une de vos sessions actives vient d'être révoquée.{{/eq}}
            </p>
            <table width="100%" style="margin:20px 0;border-collapse:collapse;">
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;width:35%;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Revoked by{{else}}Révoquée par{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;"><strong>{{revokedBy}}</strong></td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;font-size:13px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Source IP{{else}}Adresse IP source{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;font-size:14px;font-family:monospace;">{{ipAddress}}</td></tr>
            </table>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:#444;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}You will need to authenticate again on the admin console.{{else}}Vous devrez vous authentifier à nouveau sur la console d'administration.{{/eq}}
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:#E53935;margin-top:24px;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}If this revocation is unexpected (for example you did not request it), contact security@faso.bf to verify your account integrity.{{else}}Si cette révocation est inattendue (par exemple vous ne l'avez pas demandée), contactez security@faso.bf afin de vérifier l'intégrité de votre compte.{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#FFD700;padding:14px 32px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
            FASO DIGITALISATION — République du Burkina Faso<br/>
            <a href="https://faso.bf/security" style="color:#FFD700;text-decoration:underline;">https://faso.bf/security</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
